*'''Rhymes:''' [[Rhymes:English:-eɪdʒ|-eɪʤ]]

===Verb===
'''assuage''' (''past'' and ''past participle:'' [[assuaged]])
#''(intransitive)'' [[Lessen]] the intensity of; [[pacify]]; [[soothe]].
#''(transitive)'' [[Calm]] or [[appease]] (a condition or emotion); [[subside]]; [[abate]].

